OL,5, "My life is not the same," says Pamela 
OL,6, Partridge, whose husband Michael was   
OL,7, killed by a drink-driver two days after
OL,8, their 54th wedding anniversary.        
OL,10,F"I still have the card he gave me by   
OL,11,Fthe side of my bed," says Ms Partridge,
OL,12,Ffrom Caerphilly county.                
OL,14,F"I can't put that away. It's the last  
OL,15,Fcard I'll ever have off him."          
OL,17,FThe 76-year-old was cycling to a park  
OL,18,Fto meet her and their grandchildren    
OL,19,Fwhen he was hit by a van driver        
OL,20,Ftwo-and-a-half times the drink-drive   
OL,21,Flimit.                                 
